01:42:52.080 --> 01:42:52.280
I got in the car.

01:42:53.680 --> 01:42:53.880
I said, 'Well, we'll just go pray.

01:42:53.880 --> 01:42:55.200
We'll go get in the car.

01:42:55.200 --> 01:42:56.347
Paisley, let's go pray.

01:42:56.347 --> 01:42:57.520
Come on, D.

01:42:57.520 --> 01:42:59.634
Let's go get in the car.

01:42:59.634 --> 01:43:04.996
Braden, come on.

01:43:04.996 --> 01:43:08.480
We're going to go pray.

01:43:08.480 --> 01:43:15.730
' And I drove around for hours, driving around in the car, praying up and down Tulsa.

01:43:15.730 --> 01:43:21.973
'Oh, God, You're going to give me the answer.

01:43:21.973 --> 01:43:22.987
' Worship.

01:43:22.987 --> 01:43:23.662
Worship.

01:43:23.662 --> 01:43:25.140
'Oh, God, give me an answer.

01:43:25.140 --> 01:43:29.640
Paisley, you hear anything?

01:43:29.640 --> 01:43:30.540
Do you?

01:43:30.540 --> 01:43:31.440
' 'No.

01:43:31.440 --> 01:43:46.913
' But when I was at that breaking place, you know, you're just in there, and I went in and I told her, 'I'm going to go out and pull weeds.

01:43:46.913 --> 01:43:55.195
' And I was done with it.

01:44:10.423 --> 01:44:15.660
I was like, 'If You don't want to answer, it's not important to You.

01:44:15.660 --> 01:44:17.900
It's not important to me.

01:44:28.693 --> 01:44:28.996
I guess I'm not going to talk about this anymore.

01:44:28.996 --> 01:44:41.493
' And I'm out there pulling the weeds, and I'm looking at my flower in the flower bed, and I was thinking, 'Man, that's pretty amazing how fast these weeds are growing.

01:44:41.493 --> 01:44:48.068
' Pulling the weeds, and I just took my eyes off of the problem and started focusing on Him.

01:44:48.068 --> 01:44:57.396
'Well, I got to know what I'm going to say on the channel tonight.

01:44:57.396 --> 01:45:01.679
' I mean, my own personal stuff.

01:45:01.679 --> 01:45:02.880
'What do You have?

01:45:02.880 --> 01:45:05.040
' And then He spoke, and I went...

01:45:05.040 --> 01:45:08.470
It was when I took the care out of my prayer but focused it.

01:45:08.470 --> 01:45:11.849
'Be careful for nothing, but in everything with thanksgiving...

01:45:11.849 --> 01:45:21.120
' I started giving the praise to Him, and I just took it out of my subconscious mind.

01:45:21.440 --> 01:45:23.813
I stopped thinking, 'I've got to have an answer.

01:45:23.813 --> 01:45:28.870
I've got to have an answer,' and I just started worshiping Him.

01:45:28.870 --> 01:45:33.061
'Oh, You're beautiful beyond description, too marvelous for words, too wonderful for comprehension.

01:45:33.061 --> 01:45:35.687
' He knows everything you need before you need it.

01:45:49.044 --> 01:45:49.797
And He knows the things in your past—He knows everything.

01:45:49.797 --> 01:46:00.499
But He's not in the place of chaos.

01:46:00.499 --> 01:46:09.520
Sometimes He's at the snow cone stand.

01:46:09.520 --> 01:46:12.410
Sometimes He's watching something with your kids, VeggieTales or something.

01:46:12.410 --> 01:46:13.230
Laugh.

01:46:13.230 --> 01:46:15.280
He'll even say that.

01:46:15.280 --> 01:46:18.906
'I want you to laugh.

01:46:18.906 --> 01:46:21.056
' 'I don't feel like laughing.

01:46:43.360 --> 01:46:43.520
This ain't funny right now.

01:46:43.520 --> 01:46:45.222
What do You want me to laugh about?

01:46:45.222 --> 01:46:47.200
I'm not happy right now.

01:46:47.200 --> 01:46:52.765
What do You want me to laugh about?

01:46:52.765 --> 01:46:54.857
' 'I want you to laugh.

01:46:54.857 --> 01:46:58.560
' 'But Lord, this ain't funny to me.

01:46:58.560 --> 01:47:02.137
' 'I want you to laugh.

01:47:02.137 --> 01:47:06.360
I want you to enjoy life.

01:47:06.360 --> 01:47:09.360
Paisley's young right now.

01:47:09.360 --> 01:47:13.973
Go outside and play in the dirt.

01:47:13.973 --> 01:47:19.083
' 'Do You understand what I'm asking You right now?

01:47:19.083 --> 01:47:22.240
Do You not understand the pressure of life right now?

01:47:34.026 --> 01:47:34.691
I don't want to go play in the dirt.

01:47:34.691 --> 01:47:38.019
Do You get that?

01:47:38.019 --> 01:47:52.309
' But that's Him making you take your eyes off of the problem for a minute and focus on something else, and the answer comes out of it.

01:47:52.309 --> 01:47:54.560
'Play in the dirt.

01:47:54.560 --> 01:47:55.820
Do you get that?

01:47:55.820 --> 01:47:57.620
' Play in the dirt.

01:47:57.620 --> 01:47:59.520
Do you see my nails?

01:47:59.520 --> 01:48:04.040
They have dirt all in them.

01:48:04.040 --> 01:48:15.485
Literally, I had to go get my ring cleaned because I thought I popped a diamond out of my wedding ring.

01:48:15.485 --> 01:48:29.097
And I was like, 'Man,' I told D, 'I think I broke a bracket because I was digging in the dirt.

01:48:29.097 --> 01:48:51.973
' So I took it up there and they had to check it because I have a warranty on it.

01:48:51.973 --> 01:49:27.977
And I told her, 'Well, let's go up there and get it cleaned because I popped one out before and lost it because I dig in the dirt.

01:49:27.977 --> 01:49:30.730
' This is how He talks.

01:49:30.730 --> 01:49:33.240
'Get it in your nails.

01:49:33.240 --> 01:49:35.760
Get dirt all in your nails.

01:49:35.760 --> 01:49:38.339
Get it in your toes.

01:49:38.339 --> 01:49:42.935
Get mud in your toes.

01:49:42.935 --> 01:49:51.614
' And God talks.

01:49:51.614 --> 01:49:54.711
Do you get it?

01:49:54.711 --> 01:50:06.390
Some people, it may be working on your car, you know, working on your engine or something.

01:50:06.400 --> 01:50:20.035
I'm not smart enough to do that.

01:50:20.035 --> 01:50:32.340
My dad is.

01:50:32.340 --> 01:50:36.795
He can do stuff like that.

01:50:36.795 --> 01:50:48.452
My brother and other people can do it.

01:50:48.452 --> 01:51:56.719
But me, I play in the dirt and God speaks, and I love flowers.

01:52:11.379 --> 01:52:12.119
I work for a big ministry and I did their flowers.

01:52:23.920 --> 01:52:24.673
It's my deal.

01:52:41.520 --> 01:52:42.360
But I'm trying to tell you, God's not in all this.

01:52:46.752 --> 01:52:55.198
And He doesn't talk in this until you stop, 'I've got to have an answer!

01:52:55.198 --> 01:53:22.900
' He knows you've got to have an answer, but your flesh is screaming louder and He can't get through all that noise.

01:53:24.320 --> 01:53:24.959
And you know what else?

01:53:24.959 --> 01:53:27.336
And this is something else I got.

01:53:34.320 --> 01:53:34.720
I don't know why, but these little patches I got, He said, 'Put that on.

01:53:34.720 --> 01:53:53.579
' I think things are hokey, so I don't do them.

01:53:53.579 --> 01:53:57.485
But He said, 'Put that on.

01:55:18.409 --> 01:55:18.818
I want you to put that on.

01:55:18.818 --> 01:55:24.320
' And it made me feel better.

01:57:04.270 --> 01:57:04.680
And I said, 'so be it.

01:57:04.680 --> 01:57:13.990
' The answer comes when you least expect it for certain things.

01:57:18.719 --> 01:57:21.520
And He'll say, 'I want you to do this.

01:57:21.520 --> 01:58:01.757
Put that on.

01:58:01.757 --> 01:58:17.600
' And I did it.

01:58:17.600 --> 01:58:21.386
Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

01:58:21.386 --> 01:58:24.871
Do what He tells you to do.

01:58:24.871 --> 01:58:26.756
Mary said, 'Fill the pots.

01:58:26.756 --> 01:58:28.800
' They filled them to the brim with water.

01:58:28.800 --> 01:58:37.680
They got the water turned into wine and they had a miracle because they followed what He told them to do.

01:58:37.680 --> 01:58:38.960
Even when it didn't make any sense.

01:58:38.960 --> 01:58:45.453
You're going to do what?

01:58:45.453 --> 01:59:03.270
He's God, so He'll do whatever, whenever He tells you to do it.

01:59:03.270 --> 01:59:04.429
Just do it.

01:59:07.840 --> 01:59:09.184
And the answer comes out of digging in the dirt.

01:59:09.184 --> 01:59:12.910
I'm not telling you to dig in the dirt.

01:59:15.102 --> 01:59:16.916
I don't know what your thing is, you know what I'm saying?

01:59:16.916 --> 01:59:17.911
Find your box.

01:59:17.911 --> 01:59:25.269
William Seymour had to put a box on his head before the miracles would manifest in Azusa.

01:59:26.023 --> 01:59:42.657
And he put the box on his head and he waited—sometimes they said over an hour, two hours—with a box on his head.

01:59:42.657 --> 01:59:56.757
But the glory would not manifest until he put the box on his head.

01:59:56.757 --> 02:00:04.253
That's why I try to tell you all the time: find your box.

02:00:04.253 --> 02:00:05.484
What is your box?

02:01:38.544 --> 02:01:39.152
The only one that can know that is you.

02:01:39.152 --> 02:01:44.390
What is God telling you to do?

02:01:44.400 --> 02:01:57.508
I'm not trying to tell you to be a parrot and put a box on your head, but find your box, and He will speak in that box.

02:01:57.508 --> 02:02:27.383
What is it that's telling your flesh to shut up?

02:02:27.383 --> 02:02:43.640
That's where your answer is.

02:02:43.640 --> 02:02:46.949
Could be baking cookies for your kid.

02:02:46.949 --> 02:02:55.400
Could be going and not focusing on it, but just focusing on your children because they're not going to be small forever.

02:02:55.400 --> 02:02:57.739
Let's go get an ice cream.

02:02:57.739 --> 02:02:58.813
Let's go.

02:02:58.813 --> 02:03:10.480
Let's go walk in the park for just a second and throw rocks on the pond, or feed some fish or some ducks or whatever.

02:03:40.549 --> 02:03:40.777
I don't know.

02:03:40.777 --> 02:03:57.840
Taking your eyes off of your problem and putting your eyes on the beauty of life and what He's done for you already, and being thankful for what you do have and what He's already done for you, and saying, "God, thank you.

02:03:57.840 --> 02:04:00.239
God, thank you for the answer.

02:04:24.856 --> 02:04:25.119
Thank you, Lord.

02:04:25.119 --> 02:04:39.320
Thank you, Lord, that you love me enough that you died for me.

02:04:39.320 --> 02:04:47.940
Thank you, Lord, that you've never seen the righteous forsaken or his seed begging bread.

02:04:47.940 --> 02:05:04.994
" And Father, I thank you that what the devil meant for bad, God, you're going to turn it around for good.

02:05:04.994 --> 02:05:39.350
No matter what plot, no matter what plan, no matter what schemes are coming against you in the spirit realm or in the natural, everything the devil meant for bad, God will turn it in for your good if you're looking towards Him.

02:05:39.360 --> 02:05:48.742
No matter what people try to say about you, no matter what they...

02:05:48.742 --> 02:05:50.919
I'm not moved by what I see.

02:05:50.919 --> 02:05:54.040
I'm not moved by what I feel.

02:05:54.040 --> 02:05:58.227
I'm moved by what the Word says.

02:05:58.227 --> 02:06:01.660
That's where you have to stay.

02:06:01.660 --> 02:06:02.800
Stay where?

02:06:02.800 --> 02:06:08.251
In that place of, "Regardless, God, I know we know the truth.

02:06:08.251 --> 02:06:30.826
We know what you said, and you will turn it around for me.

02:06:45.520 --> 02:06:48.239
" I don't know who that was for, but that was for somebody because in my heart I hear it when I'm sitting here.

02:07:56.079 --> 02:07:57.158
I can hear that really loud: "What do I do?

02:08:06.239 --> 02:08:07.358
What do I do?

02:08:07.358 --> 02:08:12.950
What do I do?

02:08:12.960 --> 02:08:20.728
" Father, the glory.

02:08:20.728 --> 02:08:45.946
We're so grateful.

02:08:45.946 --> 02:08:50.229
Father, we lift up our president tonight.

02:08:50.229 --> 02:08:53.520
We lift him up before you, Father.

02:09:25.647 --> 02:09:26.175
We thank you, Lord, for President Trump.

02:09:26.175 --> 02:09:31.233
