02:09:31.233 --> 02:09:36.000
We apply the blood of Jesus over President Trump in this nation.

02:09:36.000 --> 02:09:43.189
We thank you, Lord, from sea to shining sea.

02:09:43.199 --> 02:09:45.440
Father, there's a covering over our nation.

02:09:45.440 --> 02:09:50.034
We pray over his children: Eric, Don Jr.

02:09:50.034 --> 02:09:51.234
, Tiffany, Barron, and Ivanka.

02:09:51.234 --> 02:09:54.640
We pray over them.

