No weapon formed against his kids will prosper.

02:10:12.259 --> 02:10:12.800
A thousand shall fall at their side and ten thousand at their right hand, but nothing shall come nigh them.

02:10:12.800 --> 02:10:15.669
Our children, Father, our kids.

02:10:15.669 --> 02:10:28.846
We thank you, Father, that as we pray for other people's kids, you haven't forgotten our children.

02:10:28.846 --> 02:10:37.353
As we sow the seeds, as we pray for Trump's kids, Father, the blessings are on ours.

02:10:37.353 --> 02:10:40.959
Thank you, Father, that you protect our children.

02:10:40.959 --> 02:10:46.000
Thank you, Lord, that they're always in the right place at the right time.

02:10:46.000 --> 02:10:54.200
We thank you, Lord, that we're training up a child in the way they should go, and when they get older, they'll not depart from it.

02:10:54.200 --> 02:11:12.239
We thank you, Lord, that our seed, our children, will be born again, filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost.

02:11:12.239 --> 02:11:16.147
We call them out of darkness and into light.

02:11:16.147 --> 02:11:37.037
We call salvation over our houses, that we will not have one child burn in hell, that every single one of them will be born again, filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost.

02:11:43.992 --> 02:11:47.409
And we believe, Father, that you've called our children for such a time as this, for a mighty move of God.

02:11:47.409 --> 02:11:57.560
Thank you, Lord, for the finances, for creative ideas to get the wealth, Father, for the wealth of the sinners laid up for the righteous.

